"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-services-and-costs-in-turkiye.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/laundry-services-costs-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey stands out not only for its academic success but also for its practical services that improve the quality of life for international students. Laundry services, in particular, are an important element that makes students’ daily lives easier. In this article, we will explore in detail the laundry options in Turkey, their prices and the advantages they offer, and help you find the best solutions for your budget and needs.<br></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="laundry-services-in-turkey-a-guide-for-international-students">Laundry Services in Turkey: A Guide for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For international students studying in Turkey, laundry services are an important part of daily life. Since students are usually on a busy schedule, they prefer to use professional services for washing and drying their clothes. Laundromats in Turkey make life easier for students by offering a hygienic and practical solution.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="types-of-laundries">Types of Laundries</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">1. <strong>Self-Washing:</strong> In this type of laundry, users can wash and dry their own laundry themselves. There is usually a fee for the use of the machine.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">2. <strong>Full Service Laundries:</strong> These laundries take care of all the laundry operations such as collection, washing, drying and delivery. Students can choose this service to save time.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">3. <strong>Specialized Washing Services:</strong> Some laundries offer washing services for special fabrics. For example, special treatments are required for wool, silk or other delicate fabrics.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="services-offered-in-laundries-in-turkey-what-to-expect">Services Offered in Laundries in Turkey: What to Expect</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Laundries in Turkey generally offer the following services:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Dry Cleaning:</strong> It is a preferred service especially for work clothes and special clothes.</li>



<li><strong>Washing and Drying:</strong> Laundromats typically offer standard washing and drying services.</li>



<li><strong>Ironing:</strong> Ironing of washed clothes is also a service offered by most laundries.</li>



<li><strong>Fast Service:</strong> Some laundromats offer fast wash and delivery options for emergencies.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For example, in a laundromat in Istanbul, the cost of washing 5 kilograms of laundry usually ranges between 4 &#8211; 8 USD, while an additional 2 &#8211; 4 USD may be charged for ironing services. Such prices may vary depending on the location of the laundromat and the services they offer.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also take a look at <a title="House Cleaning and Costs in Turkey" href="https://roadtostudy.com/">House Cleaning and Costs in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-find-the-balance-between-quality-and-price-in-laundry-services-in-turkey">How to Find the Balance Between Quality and Price in Laundry Services in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can follow the steps below to balance quality and price when choosing a laundry:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">1. <strong>Research:</strong> Research different laundries and compare prices and services they offer.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">2. <strong>Read Reviews:</strong> Find out which laundromats offer the best service by reviewing other users&#8217; experiences.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">3. <strong>Evaluate Local Recommendations:</strong> Get recommendations from friends or other students living in Turkey.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">4. <strong>Check Service Quality:</strong> Monitor the hygiene standards and customer service of laundries.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-to-consider-when-choosing-a-laundry-tips-for-international-students">What to Consider When Choosing a Laundry: Tips for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some important points to consider when choosing a laundromat:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Location:</strong> Having the laundromat close to your school or accommodation is convenient in terms of transportation.</li>



<li><strong>Pricing:</strong> Compare the prices of different laundries to find the best option for your budget.</li>



<li><strong>Range of Services:</strong> The variety of services offered will help you find a laundry that suits your needs.</li>



<li><strong>Operating Hours:</strong> The operating hours of the laundromat should suit your busy schedule.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="make-your-laundry-choice-easy-find-the-best-service-at-an-affordable-price">Make Your Laundry Choice Easy, Find the Best Service at an Affordable Price!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For international students studying in Turkey, laundry services are an important part of life. With affordable costs and quality services, students can live their daily lives more comfortably. Laundromats in Turkey make life easier for students with the various services they offer, while also helping them save money. If you are considering studying in Turkey, you should make your plans with laundry services in mind.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-reliable-are-laundry-services-in-turkey">How reliable are laundry services in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Laundry shops in Turkey generally offer hygienic and reliable services. However, it is important to study user reviews before making a choice.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-payment-methods-are-accepted-in-laundromats">What payment methods are accepted in laundromats?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most laundromats accept cash, credit cards and some accept mobile payments. However, it is worth checking the payment options before you go.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="is-it-necessary-to-make-an-appointment-for-laundry-services">Is it necessary to make an appointment for laundry services?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In general, laundries are available without an appointment. However, it may be advisable to make an appointment during peak periods.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-long-does-it-take-to-complete-laundry-services">How long does it take to complete laundry services?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The service time varies depending on the type of laundromat. Self-washing usually takes a few hours, while full-service laundries usually deliver within 24 hours.</p>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Which cities are the best for laundry services in Turkey?</h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Laundry services are more common and diverse in big cities like Istanbul, Ankara and Izmir. In these cities, there are many options for students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In the light of this information, you can better understand laundry services in Turkey and find solutions that fit your needs.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-11-09T09:09:01Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:49:26Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-services-and-costs-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Laundry services and cost guide Turkey","title":"laundry-services-and-costs-in-turkiye"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'laundry-services-costs-in-turkey';
