<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ce guide vise à vous aider à communiquer efficacement et à vous intégrer dans les espaces de vie partagés en Turquie. Chaque nouvelle expérience est une nouvelle opportunité d&#8217;apprentissage !</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2026-06-08T04:00:00Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-14T15:50:25Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/finding-roommates-and-shared-accommodation-opportunities-in-turkiye-1.webp","alt":"Students communicating and cooperating in a shared living space in Turkey","title":"finding-roommates-and-shared-accommodation-opportunities-in-turkiye"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'fr' AND "slug" = 'guide-de-la-communication-et-de-lharmonie-dans-la-vie-en-communaute-en-turquie';
